Name:           Lesser Demon
Short Name:     lesser
Level Required: 26

Description:
  Though extremely powerful, this is the weakest of all summoned demons.
  It can attack with tail lashes, fangs, and claws.

Commands:
  - summon lesser:  Summons it to you         (costs 200 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban lesser:     Banishes it               (costs 40 sp)
